OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud across
OL,6,Fthe far west will drift eastwards
OL,7,Fthroughout the night, with a little
OL,8,Fdrizzle in places, with the potential
OL,9,Ffor low cloud and murky conditions
OL,10,Fparticularly near the coast and over
OL,11,Fhills. Milder than recent nights.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FA cloudier but dry start in
OL,14,Fthe east, with the odd spot of rain
OL,15,Fpossible through the morning. Turning
OL,16,Fbrighter later perhaps with an
OL,17,Fisolated shower. Cooler than today.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
